data.description: Welcome to 263 Maryellen Drive, a 4-bedroom cape cod conveniently located near Rt. 30. With 2 bedrooms on the main floor and 2 on the second, it's layout is ideal for a variety of buyers. The bathroom features a walk-in tub and is centrally located on the main level.  Notable updates include a new electric service box installed in June 2020, as well as a brand new furnace, air conditioning unit, and water heater installed in 2023. The property also features an integral garage for added convenience. With additional updates, this property offers an excellent opportunity to turn this house into your dream home or investment property.
